*King Diamond – vocals
*Hank Shermann – guitars
*Mike Wead – guitars
*Sharlee D&#x27;Angelo – bass
*Bjarne T. Holm – drums

;Additional musicians
*Kol Marshall – keyboards

;Production
*Kol Marshall – production, engineering, mixing with Mercyful Fate
*Vince Rossi – engineering

